    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out and come take it for a spin!",
