    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in pristine showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of chips, scratches, or swirl marks, reflecting its life as a strictly garage-kept prize. Inside, the cabin retains its original allure, with premium leather upholstery showing zero signs of wear or creasing and all tactile surfaces feeling factory-fresh. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, supported by a comprehensive service history documenting a lifetime of preventative care. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained specimen that looks, smells, and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
