    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering featuring the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with preventative rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators already performed to ensure long-term reliability. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp gates, paired with an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is undisturbed, featuring a factory carbon fiber roof for a reduced polar moment of inertia and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise damping adjustments. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is up to date, and the paint retains its factory depth with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. A true turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
